 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><a style="color: #eae46f;" href="http://startupbros.com/how-to-pick-the-perfect-name-for-your-business-or-startup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Startupbros: How to pick the perfect name for your business or startup</a></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><a style="color: #eae46f;" href="https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/21774" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Entrepreneur: How to name your business</a></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><a style="color: #eae46f;" href="http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/when-it-comes-naming-your-startup-simple-better-163993" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adweek: A simple name is better</a></li>
